quran[60]{c,v,t}:
  51,1,Mi woondirii keneeli jaroray…ói (leydi) jaragol
  51,2,Mi woondirii duule ronndotoo…óe to…ìo tii…óngo
  51,3,Mi woondirii laa…óe dogiray…óe newaare
  51,4,E peccooji yamiraande
  51,5,"ko podete …óon ko, ko goongo"
  51,6,Haasbeede ko ko wonata
  51,7,Mi woondirii kammu jom …óate ngun
  51,8,"Pellet, hi…óon e konngol luurrangol"
  51,9,Hino yiltee e makko kala firlitaa…óo e gom…óinal
  51,10,Fenoo…ìe …ìen hu…óaama
  51,11,…ìen yollii…ìe e majjere welsindii…ìe
  51,12,"Hi…ìe lamndoo : \"Ko honnde woni √ëalaande njo…ìdi kuu…óe"
  51,13,√ëalaande nde …ìe leptoytee…ìe ka Yiite
  51,14,Mee…óee lepte mon …óen; ko …óum woni ko keppatno…óon kon
  51,15,"Pellet, gom…óu…ìe …ìen wonii e aljannaaji e …ìulli"
  51,16,Jaggatnoo…ìe ko Joom ma…ì…ìe okki…ìe …ìe te ko adii …óuum ko…ìe mo∆¥∆¥inatnoo…ìe
  51,17,Ho…ìe pam…óuno ko…ìe …óaanatoo jemma
  51,18,E saanga ndoogu ho…ìe toro yaafeede
  51,19,Ina e jaw…óe mumen hakke wonande √±aagatoo…ìe e …ìe √±aagataako
  51,20,Ina e nder leydi he maandeeji wonande yananaa…ìe
  51,21,E nder pittaali mon mate on teskataaka
  51,22,Ina e kammu arsuka mon e ko podante …óon
  51,23,E Joom kammu e leydi ko…óum goongo hono no kaalirton nih
  51,24,Mbela arii e maa yeewtere ho…ó…ìe Ibraahiima teddinaa…ìe
  51,25,"Tuma …ìe naatunoo ka makko …ìe wi'i: \"Salaam (Kisiyee mon)\". O maaki: \"Menen ko men …óen∆¥ii …ìe on"
  51,26,O naayii faade e koreeji makko O addori ngaari payndi
  51,27,O …ìadani…ìe ndi o wii on √±aamata
  51,28,"O so*i e mum en kulol, …ìe wii woto hul, …ìe weltiniri…ìe cuklel"
  51,29,"Jom suudu makko ari hombo wulla o hellii yeesa makko, o wii nayeejo dimara"
  51,30,Malaykaaji …ói mbii ko hono nih Joom ma daali ko Kanko woni √±ee√±o Ganndo
  51,31,"[Annabai Ibraahiima] maaki: \"Ko woni fii mon, onon …ìee nelaa…ìe"
  51,32,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Menen men nela e yim…ìe bom…ìe …ìen"
  51,33,"fii yo men accitu e ma…ì…ìe, kaa∆¥e iw…óe e loope (ju…óaa…óe)"
  51,34,"maandiniraa…óe ka Joomi maa, fii fantinoo…ìe …ìen"
  51,35,Men yaltini toon kala gom…óim…ìe wonunoo…ìe ton
  51,36,"Men tawaano ton, si wanaa suudu juul…ìe wooturu"
  51,37,"Men acci ton maande, wonannde …ìen huloo…ìe lepte muusu…óe …óen"
  51,38,"[Men acci kadi maande] e Muusaa, tuma nde Men nulunoo mo e Fir'awna, wonndude e hujja …ìanngu…óo"
  51,39,"Kono o …óuurnodii e cemmbe makko, o wi'i [Muusaa]: \"Ko mbileejo maa feetu…óo"
  51,40,"Men nanngi mo kanko e koneeli makko …óin, Men bugodii …ìe ka maayo, tawde ko o felnii…óo"
  51,41,"E 'Adi'en, tuma Men wurtunoo henndu bonndu ndun e ma…ì…ìe"
  51,42,"ndu accataa hay huunde nde ndu arani, si wanaa ndu wa…ótay nde wa ndoondi"
  51,43,"E Samuuda'en kadi, tuma nde …ìe wi'ananoo : \"Dakmitee haa see…óa"
  51,44,"∆Åe townitanii yamiroore Joomi ma…ì…ìe nden, haacaango ngon nanngi …ìe, tawi hi…ìe ∆¥eewa"
  51,45,"∆Åe waawaano daragol (laawoo), …ìe wonaano kadi faabaa…ìe"
  51,46,"Ko non kadi yim…ìe Nuuhu …ìen ko adii[…ìe]. ∆Åen ko yim…ìe faasiqii…ìe wonunoo"
  51,47,"Kammu ngun, Men mahir ngu doole Amen. Pellet, ko Men ya√±√±u…ìe"
  51,48,"Leydi ndin kan, Men weertundi. Men mo∆¥∆¥ii weertu…ìe"
  51,49,"E kala huunde, Men tagii noone …ói…ói; belajo'o on waajitoray"
  51,50,"Awa dogee kisan faade e Allah. Min, wonannde on immorde ka Makko, ko mi jertinoowo …ìanngu…óo"
  51,51,"Wata on wa…óidane Allah rewetee…óo goo. Min, wonannde on immorde ka Makko, ko mi jertinoowo …ìanngu…óo"
  51,52,"Ko wano non. Nulaa…óo araali e …ìen adinoo…ìe …ìe, si wanaa …ìe wi'ay : \"Ko mbileejo maa feetu…óo"
  51,53,"Hara …ìe wasondir e …óum? Ko woni kon, …ìee ko yim…ìe bewu…ìe"
  51,54,"Runto …ìe, a felnaaki [e fiia…ì…ìe]"
  51,55,"Waajo tun; sabu waajagol ngol, hino nafa gom…óim…ìe …ìen"
  51,56,"Mi tagiraali jinna e yim…ìe, si wanaa fii yo …ìe rewan"
  51,57,Mi …óa…ì…ìiraa …ìe arsike; Mi …óa…ì…ìaa yo …ìe √±ammina
  51,58,"Pellet, ko Allah woni arsikoowo On, Jom cemmbe tii…óu…óe"
  51,59,"Haray hino woodani …ìen too√±u…ìe, bakkaat yeru bakkaat nanndo ma…ì…ìe'en, wata …ìe hawju"
  51,60,"Bone woodanii …ìen yeddu…ìe, e nden √ëalaande ma…ì…ìe nde …ìe kammbanaa"